      • stripAndSplit

        private static java.lang.String[] stripAndSplit​(java.lang.String userInput,
                                                Action action,
                                                Actionable subject)
        Strips out the subject and all possible action aliases from a user input string, as well as common prepositions, articles and demonstrative pronouns, then splits the remaining words into an array of presumed adjectives
        Parameters:
        userInput - processed user input string
        action - the Action to use when stripping aliases from the input string
        subject - the Actionable object to use when stripping out action subjects
        Returns:
        an array of presumed adjectives present in the user input
